Usage: specifyScanCell [-help] <cellName> [-in <ftname>] [-out <ftname>]
                       [-scanClock <ftname>] [-scanEnable <ftname>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<cellName>              # name of scan cell (string, required)
-in <ftname>            # name of scan input (string, optional)
-out <ftname>           # name of scan output (string, optional)
-scanClock <ftname>     # name of scan clock (string, optional)
-scanEnable <ftname>    # name of scan enable (string, optional)